docs: This function let NFT Contract Owner to mint a new NFT without providing NFT Traits/Attributes
messages.label: mint

docs: This function let NFT Contract Owner to mint a new NFT with NFT Traits/Attributes
messages.label: mint_with_attributes

docs: This function check if an NFT is locked or not
messages.label: Psp34Traits::is_locked_nft

docs: This function sets the baseURI for the NFT contract. Only Contract Owner can perform this function. baseURI is the location of the metadata files if the NFT collection use external source to keep their NFT artwork. ArtZero uses IPFS by default, the baseURI can have format like this: ipfs://<hash_ID>/
messages.label: Psp34Traits::set_base_uri

docs: This function return how many unique attributes in the contract
messages.label: Psp34Traits::get_attribute_count

docs: This function return the metadata location of an NFT. The format is baseURI/<token_id>.json
messages.label: Psp34Traits::token_uri

docs: This function returns how many NFTs have been locked by its owners
messages.label: Psp34Traits::get_locked_token_count

docs: This function set the attributes to each NFT. Only Contract Owner can perform this function. The metadata input is an array of [(attribute, value)]. The attributes in ArtZero platform are the NFT traits.
messages.label: Psp34Traits::set_multiple_attributes

docs: This function return the latest token ID, everytime new NFT is mint, last_token_id is increased by 1 in mint function. Note: This is not the same as the total supply return by the psp34 function as NFT can be burnt.
messages.label: Psp34Traits::get_last_token_id

docs: This function return the attribute name using attribute index. Beacause attributes of an NFT can be set to anything by Contract Owner, AztZero uses this function to get all attributes of an NFT
messages.label: Psp34Traits::get_attribute_name

docs: This function lets NFT owner to lock their NFT. Once locked, the NFT traits (attributes) can not be changed
messages.label: Psp34Traits::lock

docs: This function return the owner of the NFT Contract
messages.label: Psp34Traits::get_owner

docs: This function returns all available attributes of each NFT
messages.label: Psp34Traits::get_attributes
